        },
        {
          "text": "Passive - Cooking with Fire\n\n",
          "color": "yellow"
        },
        {
          "text": "Dealing 30 cumulative damage with your frying pan will light it on fire for your next swing.\nThe lit frying pan will burn enemies, knock them back further, and give Regeneration III for 3s to nearby teammates."
        }
      ]
    }
